Description: Handle of Rhodian pottery transport amphora. Circular stamp; rose symbol. Secondary stamp on side of handle.
Curator's comments: Only known from Griffiths' drawing in Petrie's Journal, 1884-5, p.188a, 23. Name, Ippokrates'
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0811)
